{
  "video_id": "z3OykfkE_R0",
  "title": "New uses for drones - 6 Minute English",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 7780.0,
      "end_time": 10640.0,
      "text": "Rob: Hello I'm Rob and this is 6 Minute English -"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 10840.0,
      "end_time": 13300.0,
      "text": "a programme that brings you an interesting topic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 13620.0,
      "end_time": 16520.0,
      "text": "authentic listening practice and some vocabulary"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 16740.0,
      "end_time": 18779.0,
      "text": "to help you improve your language skills."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 19140.0,
      "end_time": 20400.0,
      "text": "Joining me today is Neil."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 20580.0,
      "end_time": 23279.0,
      "text": "Neil: Hello. And today we're discussing those pilotless"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 23440.0,
      "end_time": 25800.0,
      "text": "aircraft that we seem to be hearing"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 25140.0,
      "end_time": 26580.0,
      "text": "and reading a lot about at the moment."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 26880.0,
      "end_time": 29820.0,
      "text": "Rob: You mean drones. And yes, they are in the news"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 29960.0,
      "end_time": 32320.0,
      "text": "quite often for good and bad reasons."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 32820.0,
      "end_time": 34900.0,
      "text": "They've been used for many things from smuggling"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 35800.0,
      "end_time": 38160.0,
      "text": "drugs, detecting water leaks and surveillance."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 38420.0,
      "end_time": 40120.0,
      "text": "Neil: And surveillance - that means 'the act"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 40360.0,
      "end_time": 43120.0,
      "text": "of carefully watching someone or something' -"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 43500.0,
      "end_time": 46300.0,
      "text": "perhaps a criminal - but also it means spying,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 46700.0,
      "end_time": 48140.0,
      "text": "maybe on me and you Rob?"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 48500.0,
      "end_time": 49860.0,
      "text": "So should we be welcoming"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 50180.0,
      "end_time": 51660.0,
      "text": "the rise of the use of drones?"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 51960.0,
      "end_time": 54200.0,
      "text": "Rob: Well, before our discussion about that 'takes off',"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 54540.0,
      "end_time": 57120.0,
      "text": "we need to set today's question for you to answer, Neil."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 57640.0,
      "end_time": 59820.0,
      "text": "Neil: What are you droning on about Rob?"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 60220.0,
      "end_time": 62800.0,
      "text": "And by that I don't mean 'flying a drone' -"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 62220.0,
      "end_time": 64920.0,
      "text": "I mean 'talking too much in a very boring way'!"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 65180.00000000001,
      "end_time": 67540.0,
      "text": "Rob: Thanks Neil. Now just answer this, will you?"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 67900.0,
      "end_time": 70220.0,
      "text": "Drones are sometimes also referred to"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 70320.0,
      "end_time": 75179.0,
      "text": "as UAVs. So, what does UAV stand for? Is it..."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 75460.0,
      "end_time": 78380.0,
      "text": "a) Unidentified aerial vehicle,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 78840.0,
      "end_time": 81260.0,
      "text": "b) Unmanned aerial vehicle"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 81500.0,
      "end_time": 84360.0,
      "text": "or c) Unaided aircraft vehicle"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 84580.0,
      "end_time": 86640.0,
      "text": "Neil: Well, I'm going to go for b)"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 86640.0,
      "end_time": 88180.0,
      "text": "unmanned aerial vehicle."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 88400.0,
      "end_time": 91200.0,
      "text": "Rob: Ok well, we'll see if you're right later on."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 91600.0,
      "end_time": 93399.0,
      "text": "Now let's talk more about drones,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 93580.0,
      "end_time": 96480.0,
      "text": "which, apparently, seem to be everywhere now."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 96780.0,
      "end_time": 99320.0,
      "text": "Neil: But are they safe and are they necessary?"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 99840.0,
      "end_time": 102220.0,
      "text": "I've heard about them being a hazard to aircraft"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 102300.0,
      "end_time": 104300.0,
      "text": "because they've been flown close to airports."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 104660.0,
      "end_time": 107880.0,
      "text": "Rob: Well, figures in 2016 showed that in the UK"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 108100.0,
      "end_time": 111000.0,
      "text": "there were 70 near misses involving drones."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 111240.0,
      "end_time": 113339.0,
      "text": "And that's more than double the year before."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 113640.0,
      "end_time": 115400.0,
      "text": "So that is a little worrying."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 115640.0,
      "end_time": 117500.0,
      "text": "Neil: Yes. And there's the potential risk"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 117560.0,
      "end_time": 119960.0,
      "text": "of people's privacy being invaded when a drone"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 120140.0,
      "end_time": 122840.0,
      "text": "is flown over their property with a camera attached to it."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 123600.0,
      "end_time": 125680.0,
      "text": "Rob: Ah, but those cameras are also good at capturing"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 125820.0,
      "end_time": 128359.0,
      "text": "some great aerial footage - that's the film"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 128479.00000000001,
      "end_time": 130780.00000000001,
      "text": "recording of the view from the above the ground."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 131420.0,
      "end_time": 134720.0,
      "text": "So they're not all bad. And Dr Yoge Patel would agree."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 135800.0,
      "end_time": 137400.0,
      "text": "She is CEO of Blue Bear,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 137220.0,
      "end_time": 139600.0,
      "text": "which supplies unmanned planes and drones."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 139920.0,
      "end_time": 142380.0,
      "text": "Here she is speaking about drones on the BBC's"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 142560.0,
      "end_time": 143800.0,
      "text": "Woman's Hour programme..."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 144300.0,
      "end_time": 145240.0,
      "text": "Dr Yoge Patel: They have the potential"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 145240.0,
      "end_time": 147880.0,
      "text": "to be dangerous, agreed. They also have though,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 148400.0,
      "end_time": 151299.0,
      "text": "on the flip side, the ability to be a game changer"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 151500.0,
      "end_time": 155200.0,
      "text": "in both domestic use and in military use."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 155560.0,
      "end_time": 156880.0,
      "text": "So, some of our drones are being used"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 156920.0,
      "end_time": 159239.0,
      "text": "for aircraft inspections. We've put our drones"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 159340.0,
      "end_time": 160160.0,
      "text": "into Fukishima."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 160760.0,
      "end_time": 163739.0,
      "text": "Rob: So there you go Neil. There are many useful things"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 163840.0,
      "end_time": 166400.0,
      "text": "drones can do, and Dr Patel said"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 166240.0,
      "end_time": 168740.0,
      "text": "they have the ability to be a game changer."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 169200.0,
      "end_time": 170240.0,
      "text": "Neil: And by that you mean 'something that"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 170500.0,
      "end_time": 172680.0,
      "text": "completely changes the way something is done"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 172920.0,
      "end_time": 173760.0,
      "text": "or thought about'."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 173980.0,
      "end_time": 176780.0,
      "text": "Rob: Yes. Her company has used drones to inspect"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 176940.0,
      "end_time": 179440.0,
      "text": "the inside of the damaged Fukishima nuclear"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 179640.0,
      "end_time": 180940.0,
      "text": "power station in Japan."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 181500.0,
      "end_time": 184400.0,
      "text": "And another example of drones being a game changer"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 184220.0,
      "end_time": 186859.0,
      "text": "is UNICEF and the Malawian government testing drones"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 187600.0,
      "end_time": 188640.0,
      "text": "for carrying medical supplies."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 189320.0,
      "end_time": 191660.0,
      "text": "This could help save lives in remote places."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 192600.0,
      "end_time": 193500.0,
      "text": "Neil: And I have read that in Australia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 193720.0,
      "end_time": 195960.0,
      "text": "lifeguards are using drones to help rescue"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 196200.0,
      "end_time": 197920.0,
      "text": "swimmers who get in trouble in the sea."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 198260.0,
      "end_time": 200500.0,
      "text": "Rob: And have you heard about a Japanese firm"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 200680.0,
      "end_time": 203500.0,
      "text": "that's planning to use a drone to force employees"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 203660.0,
      "end_time": 206320.0,
      "text": "out of their offices by playing music at them"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 206380.0,
      "end_time": 208519.0,
      "text": "if they stay to work evening overtime."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 208720.0,
      "end_time": 210260.0,
      "text": "Neil: I haven't, but you've convinced me -"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 210500.0,
      "end_time": 212180.0,
      "text": "it seems like the sky's the limit"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 212400.0,
      "end_time": 213420.0,
      "text": "for the uses of drones!"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 213720.0,
      "end_time": 215980.0,
      "text": "I mean there's no limit to what they can do."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 216500.0,
      "end_time": 217880.0,
      "text": "But I am a little concerned"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 217980.0,
      "end_time": 219959.0,
      "text": "about how they are regulated or controlled."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 220240.0,
      "end_time": 223200.0,
      "text": "Rob: Well Dr Yoge Patel says because the technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 223260.0,
      "end_time": 226320.0,
      "text": "is new, regulations - or legal controls -"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 226560.0,
      "end_time": 228200.0,
      "text": "are developing all the time..."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 228660.0,
      "end_time": 231340.0,
      "text": "Dr Yoge Patel: As technology progresses, regulation"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 231540.0,
      "end_time": 234299.0,
      "text": "and operational use needs to then be harmonised"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 234460.0,
      "end_time": 237400.0,
      "text": "with it. And we are, as a community, going through"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 237280.0,
      "end_time": 239380.0,
      "text": "that whole process of saying what is"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 239660.0,
      "end_time": 241859.0,
      "text": "proportionate and appropriate regulation"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 242000.0,
      "end_time": 244980.0,
      "text": "to go with different uses of drones."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 245360.0,
      "end_time": 247280.0,
      "text": "Neil: So she talked about regulations being"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 247520.0,
      "end_time": 249460.0,
      "text": "harmonised as technology progresses."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 249800.0,
      "end_time": 252360.0,
      "text": "Rob: So I think she means 'making regulations suitable"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 252620.0,
      "end_time": 254520.0,
      "text": "and appropriate for what the drones"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 254700.0,
      "end_time": 257380.0,
      "text": "are being used for'. So they need some control,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 257600.00000000003,
      "end_time": 259980.00000000003,
      "text": "but not so they can't be useful and effective."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 260300.0,
      "end_time": 262800.0,
      "text": "Neil: Like flying drones to stop you working late!"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 263200.0,
      "end_time": 264140.0,
      "text": "Now Rob, I'm dying to know"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 264460.0,
      "end_time": 265979.0,
      "text": "what the other name for a drone is."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 266220.0,
      "end_time": 268720.0,
      "text": "Rob: OK, let me tell you. So earlier I asked you"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 268760.0,
      "end_time": 271240.0,
      "text": "what does UAV stand for? Was it..."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 271480.0,
      "end_time": 273840.0,
      "text": "a) Unidentified aerial vehicle"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 274800.0,
      "end_time": 276120.0,
      "text": "b) Unmanned aerial vehicle"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 276520.0,
      "end_time": 279299.0,
      "text": "or c) Unaided aircraft vehicle"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 279640.0,
      "end_time": 282180.0,
      "text": "Neil: And I said b) - was that correct?"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 282540.0,
      "end_time": 285200.0,
      "text": "Rob: Yes Neil, you know your drones - that's correct."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 285420.0,
      "end_time": 288660.0,
      "text": "Well done. UAVs or drones have been around"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 288660.0,
      "end_time": 290520.0,
      "text": "for quite a while in different forms."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 290860.0,
      "end_time": 293360.0,
      "text": "It's thought they were first used for providing"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 293580.0,
      "end_time": 296580.0,
      "text": "practice targets for training military personnel."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 296800.0,
      "end_time": 299220.0,
      "text": "OK Neil, let's quickly go over some of the"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 299220.0,
      "end_time": 301400.0,
      "text": "vocabulary we have mentioned today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 301240.0,
      "end_time": 302900.0,
      "text": "starting with surveillance."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 303220.0,
      "end_time": 304760.0,
      "text": "Neil: \"The police kept the jewellery shop"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 305400.0,
      "end_time": 307320.0,
      "text": "under surveillance because they had a tip-off"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 307340.0,
      "end_time": 309599.0,
      "text": "about a robbery.\" So that means 'carefully"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 309600.0,
      "end_time": 310740.0,
      "text": "watching someone or something,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 311200.0,
      "end_time": 314000.0,
      "text": "usually to try to stop something illegal'."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 314800.0,
      "end_time": 316660.0,
      "text": "Rob: Then we mentioned aerial footage -"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 316940.0,
      "end_time": 319240.0,
      "text": "that's film recording made from the sky."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 319620.0,
      "end_time": 322300.0,
      "text": "\"The aerial footage on TV of the dolphins swimming"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 322500.0,
      "end_time": 323500.0,
      "text": "was spectacular.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 323660.0,
      "end_time": 325840.0,
      "text": "Neil: Yes, drones have been a game changer"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 326100.0,
      "end_time": 328600.0,
      "text": "for wildlife programmes on TV. That means"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 328800.0,
      "end_time": 330680.0,
      "text": "'something that completely changes the way"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 330680.0,
      "end_time": 332500.0,
      "text": "something is done or thought about'."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 332980.0,
      "end_time": 335800.0,
      "text": "Rob: We also mentioned the phrase 'the sky's the limit',"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 336140.0,
      "end_time": 337580.0,
      "text": "meaning 'there's no limit to something'."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 337980.0,
      "end_time": 339780.0,
      "text": "\"The sky is the limit to what professional"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 339780.0,
      "end_time": 341299.0,
      "text": "footballers can earn these days.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 341720.0,
      "end_time": 343420.0,
      "text": "Neil: Then we discussed harmonised -"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 343480.0,
      "end_time": 346600.0,
